Vans Sk8-Hi MTE 2.0 DX Valerian White (W)
results.story: The Vans Sk8-Hi MTE 2.0 DX “Valerian/True White” is a pair of rugged, water-resistant high-tops from the California-based footwear brand. Vans uses their popular Sk8-Hi model as the inspiration behind a special remaking for inclement weather. The aforementioned water-resistant upper features purple leather eyelets as well as a tonal forefoot and mid-panel. Tonal water-proof suede covers the collar and heel. Vans outfits the durable shoe with their classic white leather jazzy stripe and includes a small branding tag near the collar. The inner is lined with an extra layer of warm to keep things extra cozy on those particularly frigid winter days. Completing the design is a white rubber midsole with a gum traction bottom that assists in conquering snow, slush and anything else that is thrown its way.

Disney x Wmns Slide-On 'Minnie's Bow'
results.story: While Disney tapped Vans for a collection celebrating the 90th anniversary of Mickey Mouse, the Slide-On ‘Minnie’s Bow’ pays homage to Mickey’s significant other, Minnie Mouse. The character’s signature red and white polka dots are recreated on the strap, which is topped with a stuffed bow. A molded PU footbed in contrast black is printed with dual Vans and Disney branding.

results.colorway: Mickey Mouse And Minnie Mouse/Checker Flame
results.story: Drawing from the rich archive of Mickey Mouse designs, Disney and Vans partnered up to celebrate the legendary character’s 90th-anniversary. The Disney x Slip-On 'Mickey & Minnie' features a canvas upper dressed in a black and white checkerboard color scheme. The low top also boasts flame designs on the side panel, a padded collar for comfort, a large Mickey Mouse head printed on the toe box, and a vulcanized outsole for flexibility and superior traction.

Marvel x Wmns Slide-On 'Multi Women'
results.story: The Marvel x Slide-On 'Multi Women' features a black PU footbed stamped with Vans and Marvel branding. The underside of the synthetic leather straps are lined with foam-backed soft neoprene, while the top showcases the women of Marvel in an allover black-and-white print. This slide is a women’s exclusive model.

results.name: Vans Authentic Marvel Avengers (W)
results.story: Vans joins forces with Marvel Comics for the Vans x Marvel collection—a celebration of Marvel Universe superheroes across different franchises. Released in June 2018, the Marvel x Authentic 'Marvel Women' sneaker is emblazoned with an allover print showcasing Marvel’s female protagonists on a signature canvas upper. A hit of red accents the ‘Off The Wall’ bumper logo at the heel and printed lining, while a rubber waffle outsole complements the design.

results.name: Vans Slip-On Checker Floral (W)
results.story: The Vans Classic Slip-On 'Checker Floral' sneaker was released in April 2018, offering a feminine take on the iconic skate style from 1977. This low-key shoe features a black canvas upper with checkerboard-patterned elastic insets for easier on and off. The top of the design is embellished with embroidered flowers, cherries, leaves and a butterfly. Following tradition, the style is founded on a cushioned autoclave sole with Waffle-inspired rubber tread.

Vans Old Skool Retro Sport Blossom (W)
results.story: A revamp on an old-time classic, the Old Skool Retro Sport features a pink suede upper with visible stitching, a reinforced toe cap for durability and support, and a padded collar for extra comfort and an adaptive fit. The low top also boasts contrasting white accents on the Vans branding and on the signature chunky midsole.
